                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8709" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0209</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2043 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">数链同心：洪九果品数字供应链助力价值共创</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Digital Supply Chain Synergy: Hongjiu Fruit&#39;s Digital Supply Chain Empowers Value Co-creation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钟廷勇，冷莉玲，蔡梓轩，陈欢，周宁</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆洪九果品股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">鲜果分销行业； 数字化供应链 ；数字化转型； 供应链成本；2024百优案例；西部专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Fruit distribution; Industry digital supply chain;Digital transformation; Supply chain cost</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">伴随着全球企业数字化转型的深入推进，数字技术与供应链融合不断深化，展现出了巨大赋能作用，数字化供应链已成为产业界应对供应链风险挑战的重要探索方向。本案例描述了重庆洪九果品股份有限公司（以下简称洪九果品）将数字技术融入企业“端到端”供应链中，打通鲜果分销企业采购、在途管理和销售等全价值链环节，推动上中下游全产业链联动，实现全产业链、全价值链生态化协作的过程。本案例旨在引导学生思考企业供应链数字化的战略性问题:包括数字供应链的定义，企业搭建数字化供应链的具体路径，探讨数字化成熟度模型如何精准评估企业数字供应链成效，并进一步探究数字化供应链助力企业价值共创的内在机制。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the deepening of digital transformation in global enterprises, the
 integration of digital technology and supply chain has been constantly strengthened,
 demonstrating significant enabling effects. Digital supply chain has become a crucial
 exploration direction for the industry to address supply chain risks and challenges.
 This case study describes how Chongqing Hongjiu Fruit Co., Ltd. (hereinafter
 referred to as Hongjiu Fruit) integrates digital technology into the &quot;end-to-end&quot; supply
 chain, connects all value chain links including procurement, in-transit management,
 and sales in the fresh fruit distribution industry, promotes upstream, midstream, and
 downstream industrial chain collaboration, and achieves ecological collaboration
 throughout the entire industrial chain and value chain. This case aims to guide
 students to reflect on strategic issues related to enterprise supply chain digitization,
 including the connotation and transformation motivation of digital supply chain,
 specific approaches for fresh fruit distributors to build digital supply chain, how to
 evaluate enterprise supply chain using a digital maturity model, and explore the
 internal mechanism of digital supply chain assisting enterprises in value co-creation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链管理》、《运营管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">价值链理论；数字供应链；供应链数字化转型路径；数字成熟度模型；价值共创理论；利益相关者理论；</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
